{
  "stem": "13382.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, I mean, pinching or stealing it was holy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Today, they put you into jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But back then you were a hero.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You can't-- you can sort of steal something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So as we were packing those trucks from the-- from the wagon, we had to say loudly [NON-ENGLISH] 1, 2, 3.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But when it comes, you always picked up somehow the-- needless to say that there was always one bag of flour more than-- than we should have.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was in cooperation with the driver.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we passed a school, [INAUDIBLE], where we lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they already knew that we passing there, so we just throw one bag of flour down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had a bag of flour.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it happened with-- with a few other things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think butter was the premium at that time in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So a consignment of Austrian [INAUDIBLE] butter in round-- round tin can from United Nations organization.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said to-- to pinch a butter, a box of butter, which I think must have been two dozen-- it's a fortune.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because for that time, anything which was edible-- I mean, the people were giving homes away, houses away just-- just for food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was such a terrible situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the same thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We succeeded to-- to pinch one box of Australian butter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the butter inside the tin had no sort of printed seal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it just ordinary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just a tin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we made some inquiry, what can we do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somebody was suggesting that there is a baker, an Austrian baker somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he's a-- sort of a-- on the black market-- black market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He's going to buy it off you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we took two boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We took that butter over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we didn't know how much.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
